{"sha": "6c0b779b7bb23ad1bead914e8023642cc2368406", "node_id": "MDY6Q29tbWl0NzI0NzEyOjZjMGI3NzliN2JiMjNhZDFiZWFkOTE0ZTgwMjM2NDJjYzIzNjg0MDY=", "commit": {"author": {"name": "bors", "email": "bors@rust-lang.org", "date": "2020-02-01T11:41:05Z"}, "committer": {"name": "bors", "email": "bors@rust-lang.org", "date": "2020-02-01T11:41:05Z"}, "message": "Auto merge of #68698 - tmiasko:catch-panic, r=Amanieu\n\nRemove incorrect debug assertions from catch_unwind\n\nPreviously the debug assertions in the implementation of catch_unwind\nused to verify consistency of the panic count by checking that the count\nis zero just before leaving the function. This incorrectly assumed that\nno panic was in progress when entering `catch_unwind`.\n\nFixes #68696.", "tree": {"sha": "09c774110cf308364aa834450c9bce8550fd10f8", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/trees/09c774110cf308364aa834450c9bce8550fd10f8"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/commits/6c0b779b7bb23ad1bead914e8023642cc2368406", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": false, "reason": "unsigned", "signature": null, "payload": null}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/6c0b779b7bb23ad1bead914e8023642cc2368406", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/commit/6c0b779b7bb23ad1bead914e8023642cc2368406", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/6c0b779b7bb23ad1bead914e8023642cc2368406/comments", "author": {"login": "bors", "id": 3372342, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjMzNzIzNDI=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3372342?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors", "html_url": "https://github.com/bors", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "sub